    Yields on savings-type certificates of deposit dropped slightly
    last week. 
  </text>
  <arg n="1">Yields on savings-type certificates of deposit</arg>
  <rel>dropped</rel>
  <arg f="MNR" n="2">slightly</arg>
  <arg f="TMP" n="M">last week</arg>
</example>

